keyPolicies.policyTitle: Culling of badgers for control of Bovine TB
keyPolicies.policyDescription: UKIP supports the trial culling of badgers for control of Bovine TB, if veterinary opinion substantiates it.
UKIP will impose stronger controls on bush meat.
UKIP supports the principle of science before emotion on any agricultural topic.
Additional agricultural policies are being developed with the interests of UK farmers being the top priority.
